objects.name: controls_for_devs_and_playtest
objects.string:
Controls (for playtesters/devs)
Camera: WASD (Shift for speed CTRL for slow)
Click to Place Current Object
Move your Cursor to the Left Side of the Screen to Select a new Object
Shift+Right Click an Object to Delete (Gonna Change)
GRID SIZING:
Shift to do a 1:1 grid size for placement
CTRL to do 8:8 grid size for placement
Nothing to do 4:4  grid size for placement
Thats it (Click text to Hide, or autohides after 15 seconds)
